From 15de44e8226194377a344655b8f6fcf8d01afd32 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Wed, 11 Feb 2026 08:27:19 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 01/42] Add One Profile app: Content Shell clone at 60fps
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

A shell by any other name would frame as sweet—
We copied every file, renamed each street.
Three build snags rose: visibility, resources, tests,
But sixty frames per second passed our quests.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
